OL,3,CPrisons minister says community orders
OL,4,Cneed to be 'trusted more' by courts
OL,6,F"Doing this job comes with a health
OL,7,Fwarning," Prisons Minister Lord James
OL,8,FTimpson joked. "The number of people
OL,9,Fwho have come up to me and said: 'How
OL,10,Fare you?'"
OL,12,FAs CEO of the Timpson Group, Mr
OL,13,FTimpson gained public recognition for
OL,14,Fhis company's decision to hire
OL,15,Fhundreds of ex-offenders within his
OL,16,Fstores.
OL,18,FNow a government minister within the
OL,19,FMinistry of Justice, tackling prison
OL,20,Fcapacity and reoffending are among the
OL,21,Flong list of challenges in his in-tray.
