OL,3,CPrisons minister says community orders
OL,4,Cneed to be 'trusted more' by courts
OL,6,FMany campaigners hoped his appointment
OL,7,Fwould mark a gear shift in how the
OL,8,Fjustice system rehabilitates prisoners
OL,9,Fand supports victims.
OL,11,FHis first few months have been a
OL,12,Fbaptism of fire, coinciding with an
OL,13,Fovercrowding crisis in which some male
OL,14,Fprisons were running at over 99
OL,15,Fpercent capacity - a problem
OL,16,Fcompounded by recent riots that saw
OL,17,Fmore than 1,000 people arrested.
