OL,6,FMr Timpson has, throughout his short
OL,7,Ftenure, kept a relatively low public
OL,8,Fprofile, but speaking at an event
OL,9,Fhosted by the Fabian Society at Labour
OL,10,FParty conference, he outlined his
OL,11,Fvision for the role.
