OL,3,CPrisons minister says community orders
OL,4,Cneed to be 'trusted more' by courts
OL,6,F"I'm in this for the long haul, and I
OL,7,Fhope by putting me in this position
OL,8,Fthe prime minister has sent a signal
OL,9,Fthat we need to change the system and
OL,10,FI'm hopefully going to be around long
OL,11,Fenough to do it," he told attendees.
OL,13,F"We need a probation service that has
OL,14,Fenough staff that are trained, that
OL,15,Fare experienced and we need to work
OL,16,Falongside the courts," he added.
OL,18,FHe was directly challenged by the
OL,19,Faudience on the need to use community
OL,20,Forders more as alternatives to prison.
