OL,6,FHe also said he recognised the
OL,7,Fimportance of bringing the public
OL,8,Fonside and restoring confidence in the
OL,9,Fsystem.
OL,11,F"When it comes to the point on the
OL,12,Fview of the public, this is something
OL,13,Fthat I am really aware of because not
OL,14,Feverybody will have my view on what
OL,15,Fprisons are for but we need to make
OL,16,Fsure that everything we do cuts crime,
OL,17,Fif it cuts crime and reduces
OL,18,Freoffending then I hope the public
OL,19,Fwill follow us."
