OL,6,FHis message was one of determined
OL,7,Foptimism, admitting to the audience
OL,8,Fthat there was "a lot to do".
OL,10,FBut he also reflected on the impact of
OL,11,Fthe summer riots, sparked by the fatal
OL,12,Fstabbing of three young girls in
OL,13,FSouthport, and warned of the dangers
OL,14,Fof continuing to run an overheated
OL,15,Fprisons system without reform.
