OL,3,CPrisons minister says community orders
OL,4,Cneed to be 'trusted more' by courts
OL,6,F"One of the key lessons is you can't
OL,7,Frun prisons at 99.7 per cent full when
OL,8,Fyou then have civil disobedience like
OL,9,Fwe had and you get to a point where
OL,10,Fthere is less than 100 spaces left in
OL,11,Fthe whole prison estate in England and
OL,12,FWales," he said.
OL,14,F"It is dangerous and it means the
OL,15,Fpolice and courts can't do their job."
OL,17,F"We were lucky that we just had enough
OL,18,Fspaces and we can't run it that hot in
OL,19,Fthe future."
